      {
        "type": "rule",
        "text": "In your Shooting phase , after this model has shot, select one enemy unit (excluding MONSTERS and VEHICLES ) hit by one or more of those attacks made with squig-launchas and roll one D6: on a 4+, until the end of your opponent\u2019s next turn, that enemy unit is hindered. While a unit is hindered, subtract 2\" from its Move characteristic and subtract 2 from Advance and Charge rolls made for it.",
        "name": "Buzzer Squigs"
      },
      {
        "type": "rule",
        "text": "Once per battle, at the start of any phase , select one enemy unit within 3\" of this model and roll one D6: on a 4+, that enemy unit suffers D6 mortal wounds .",
        "name": "Squig Mine"
      },
      {
        "type": "rule",
        "text": "Place a Squig Mine token next to the model, removing it once this ability has been used.",
